#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:3
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_pointer\"]"
msgstr "Tip: You can use it to play with your cat. And your drones too."

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:4
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_siphon\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: This beam does no damage, but transfers enemy shields to you, "
"supershields included. Use it for offence, defence, or both!"

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:5
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_refractor\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: Refractor beams can pierce any amount of shields, but refraction "
"offsets the target point the stronger the shields are."

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:6
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_beam_shotgun\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: The pinpoint array fires 9 pinpoint beams at once. Has 2 modes: "
"[Pattern] fires beams in 3x3 grid with 1 tile spacing, while [Scatter] fires"
" them randomly in a radius."

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:7
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_focus_hack\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: This beam can't pierce any shields, but it can effectively keep a "
"system under constant hack if shields are down. Also mind controls any crew "
"hit!"

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:8
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_howitzers\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: Howitzers are a cross between beam and missile weapons. They use "
"missiles to fire, target in a radius similar to flak, can partially pierce "
"shields and generally inflict heavy damage."

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:9
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_disintegrators\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: Disintegrators are special beams designed by Lily using Eldritch "
"technology. They apply their damage over time to crew and systems, as well "
"as severely impeding healing and repairs, and will damage hull when hitting "
"breached rooms. The effects apply even to resistant rooms or when hitting "
"shield bubbles!"

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:10
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_disintegrators_alt\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: Disintegrators are special beams designed by Lily using Eldritch "
"technology. They apply their damage over time to crew and systems, as well "
"as severely impeding healing and repairs, and will damage hull when hitting "
"fully destroyed systems. The effects apply even to resistant rooms or when "
"hitting shield bubbles!"

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:12
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_syringe\"]"
msgstr "Tip: Special beam weapon. Need to be configured before use."

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:13
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_syringe_m\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: Applies 4/s healing for 15 second for allied crew. Also halves damage "
"taken from hazards for the duration."

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:14
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_syringe_s\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: Provides doubled movement speed and damage for 10 seconds for allied "
"crew."

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:15
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_syringe_p\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: Does 4 hp/s damage for 25 seconds for any crew hit, doesn't stack. "
"Lethal for most races in ships without any medical facilities."

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:16
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_lily_syringe_a\"]"
msgstr ""
"Tip: Applies weak erosion effect for every tile hit. Also does 10 hp/s "
"damage for 3 seconds for any crew hit."

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:19
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"button_lily_beam\"]"
msgstr "E. BLAST"

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:20
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"button_lily_ion\"]"
msgstr "ION"

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:22
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"map_icon_beam_emporium\"]"
msgstr "BEAM EMPORIUM"

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:24
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"lily_aether_submit\"]"
msgstr ""
"You watch as a rift in space opens and consumes the item you have given.\n"
"\"Nice find, this will do perfectly--\""

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:26
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"lily_aether_redeem\"]"
msgstr ""
"You watch as a rift in space opens and gives you a brand new Aether weapon!\n"
"\"And here's a reward for all your troubles--\""

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:29
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"loot_zoltan_2\"]"
msgstr ""
"ZOLTAN LOOT\n"
"Does additional damage to systems\n"
"-1 second cooldown, +20% breach chance"

#: src-en/data/text_misc.xml.append:36
msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"credit_victory_nexus_her_lily\"]"
msgstr ""
"Power unmatched, and with The One Who Rhymes, Lily, and yourself by Her "
"side, She returns to the Nexus and eradicates the remaining forces of the "
"C.E.L. Your original mission is instantly forgotten, as a new dark empire "
"descends on the Multiverse, spreading madness through the infinite expanse "
"of the cosmos for eternity."
